title: New York Annual Digest
additional-notes: Renewals for this publication appear in the Books section of the CCE rather than in the Periodicals section.  Active renewals appear starting in the July-December 1956 CCE volume, but the earliest actively renewed issue is noted in the January-June 1957 CCE volume.
We are not certain of the exact relation this publication has with New York Digest or Abbott New York Digest.
